metadata.name: Dreaming Armistice Day#5
metadata.description:
Dreaming Armistice Day by Adigitalscenesart
Anyone who has lived through the horrors of war 
knows how important the day when the conflicts end is. 
On that day, that incredible feeling appears in the air
 as if you are dreaming and floating through magical worlds, 
because if you have experienced horror and fear, 
knowing that it is now over is something indescribable. 
You simply have to live the moment and life. 
This is for all those who didn't get this chance.
